flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Create New Empty Workstation]
    B --> C[Create Slide Table<br/>(Rectangular Body)]
    C --> D[Set Slide Table Dimensions<br/>2000 × 500 × 100 mm]
    D --> E[Set Slide Table Color<br/>(Yellow)]
    E --> F[Create Slider]
    F --> G[Set Slider Dimensions<br/>400 × 400 × 100 mm]
    G --> H[Set Slider Color<br/>(Green)]
    H --> I[Rename Components<br/>Slide Table & Slider]
    I --> J[Create Mechanical Device Model]
    J --> K[Set Slide Table as BaseLink]
    K --> L[Set Slider as Link (L2)]
    L --> M[Create Linear Joint]
    M --> N[Define Motion Direction]
    N --> O[Set Joint Limits<br/>0 – 1500 mm]
    O --> P[Compile the Mechanism]
    P --> Q[Add Position Data]
    Q --> R[Set Motion Time]
    R --> S[Test Motion Using Manual Joints]
    S --> T[Save as Library File]
    T --> U[Import Mechanical Device<br/>Into Other Workstations]
    U --> V([End])
